        return submission;
    }

    if (!isInstructor && !isTeachingAssistant) {
        throw new ForbiddenException("Not authorized to access this submission");
    }
    throw new ForbiddenException("Not authorized to access this submission");
}
```

**THE BUG:** Lines 139-141:
- If the user is a TA or Instructor but NONE of the specific conditions matched (not student owner, not quiz owner, not assigned as grader), the code STILL reaches line 139
