- **testPublishContent()** (lines 115-131): Tests content publication workflow

**NO ISSUES FOUND** with the test itself. All assertions are correct, mocks are properly configured, and test cases cover the main functionality.

---

### **ISSUE 5: Backend config classes**

**Files reviewed completely:**
- `/Users/mac/Documents/EaglePoint/TASK-49/repo/backend/src/main/java/com/scholarops/config/EncryptionConfig.java`
- `/Users/mac/Documents/EaglePoint/TASK-49/repo/backend/src/main/java/com/scholarops/config/SecurityConfig.java`
- `/Users/mac/Documents/EaglePoint/TASK-49/repo/backend/src/main/java/com/scholarops/config/JacksonConfig.java`
- `/Users/mac/Documents/EaglePoint/TASK-49/repo/backend/src/main/java/com/scholarops/config/AsyncConfig.java`
