      Map<String, String> fieldErrors = ex.getBindingResult().getFieldErrors().stream()
              .collect(Collectors.toMap(
                      fe -> fe.getField(),  // Returns actual field names
                      fe -> fe.getDefaultMessage()...
  ```

  Validation errors reveal entity field names (`passwordHash`, `correctAnswer`, etc.), which aids reconnaissance.

