### **6. STUDENT QUIZ RETRIEVAL EXPOSES CORRECT ANSWERS BEFORE SUBMISSION**

#### **Issue 6.1: QuizPaper Endpoint Returns All Question Data Including Answers**
- **Location**: `/Users/mac/Documents/EaglePoint/TASK-49/repo/backend/src/main/java/com/scholarops/service/QuizAssemblyService.java` (lines 115-118)
